<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IFRS01_39T"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>39T</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS&#xa0;1"/><data name="paranum" value="39T"/></prolog><body><variant base="F53628051" id="IFRS01_39T_V2"> <p id="IFRS01_P0197"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to <xref base="F53628053" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0337">IFRS&#xa0;10</xref>, <xref base="F53628054" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0338">IFRS&#xa0;12</xref> and <xref base="F53628055" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0339">IAS&#xa0;27</xref>), issued in October 2012, amended paragraphs <xref base="F53628056" href="IFRS01_D16.dita#IFRS01_D16/IFRS01_D16_V2" id="IFRS01_X0340">D16</xref>, <xref base="F53628057" href="IFRS01_D17.dita#IFRS01_D17/IFRS01_D17_V2" id="IFRS01_X0341">D17</xref> and <xref base="F53628058" href="IFRS01_APPC.dita#IFRS01_APPC" id="IFRS01_X0342">Appendix C</xref>. An entity shall apply those amendments for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2014. Earlier application of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> is permitted. If an entity applies those amendments earlier it shall also apply all amendments included in <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> at the same time.</p></variant></body></paragraph>